OL,3,CCollision closes Lisnevenagh Road in
OL,4,CBallymena
OL,6,FThe Lisnevenagh Road in Ballymena is
OL,7,Fclosed in both directions from the
OL,8,FSeven Towers Roundabout to the
OL,9,FDunsilly Roundabout due to a collision.
OL,11,FPolice are advising road users to seek
OL,12,Fan alternative route for their journey.
OL,14,FSign up for our free weekly newsletter
OL,15,Fhere.
